<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
			<h2 class="centered dark-blue-text">Pre-Register Today</h2>
			<h4 class="centered dark-red-text">Be part of the Future Americans. Create a Safer America!</h4>
			<h6 class="centered"><em><strong>Launching Late September 2016</strong></em></h6>
			<p class="charcoal-text centered" style="font-size: 16px;">
				Imagine <strong class="medium-blue-text">millions of Americans</strong> that have signed up to help others.  Millions of good hearted people who are <strong>willing to help your family</strong>.
				<strong>These Special Volunteers</strong> are “<strong class="light-red-text">American Deputies</strong>” who have sworn <strong>to help others in need</strong>.  <strong class="medium-blue-text">Our goal is to have 10 million American Deputies</strong>!
				<br><br>
				<strong class="medium-blue-text">So when you or your child is in trouble</strong>, these <strong class="light-red-text">American Deputies</strong> are <strong>instantly notified</strong> through the <strong>APP</strong>.
				<strong>Again, like Uber, they see you and your location</strong> on their smart phones and can <strong class="medium-blue-text">quickly come to your aid</strong>.
				They may be only <strong class="medium-blue-text">seconds or minutes away</strong>.
			</p>

			<hr>

			<%= simple_form_for @data, url: send_form_path, method: :post do |f| %>
				<%= f.error_notification %>

				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-sm-12">
						<%= f.input :member_type, as: :radio_buttons, collection: [['I want to be a Deputy', 'Deputy'], ['I want the App for my Family', 'Family'], ['I want Both', 'Both']], label: 'What Are You Interested In?' %>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-4" style="margin: 10px 0;">
						<%= f.input :first_name, placeholder: 'John', label: 'First Name' %>
					</div>
					<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-4" style="margin: 10px 0;">
						<%= f.input :middle_name, placeholder: 'Tildon', label: 'Middle Name' %>
					</div>
					<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-4" style="margin: 10px 0;">
						<%= f.input :last_name, placeholder: 'Smith', label: 'Last Name' %>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6" style="margin: 5px 0;">
						<%= f.input :email, placeholder: 'john@domain.com' %>
					</div>
					<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6" style="margin: 5px 0;">
						<%= f.input :phone, placeholder: '214-990-0022' %>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-4" style="margin: 5px 0 10px;">
						<%= f.input :street1, placeholder: '1135 Main St.', label: 'Street' %>
					</div>
					<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-4" style="margin: 5px 0 10px;">
						<%= f.input :street2, placeholder: 'Suite 112', label: 'Street 2' %>
					</div>
					<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-4" style="margin: 5px 0 10px;">
						<%= f.input :zipcode, placeholder: '75244' %>
					</div>
				</div>

				<%= f.submit 'PRE-REGISTER NOW', class: 'btn btn-red btn-lg btn-primary btn-default', style: 'width: 100%; margin-top: 12px;' %>

			<% end %>

			<p class="charcoal-text centered" style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 10px;">
				<strong class="medium-blue-text">Now, you are not alone.</strong>
				We are <strong class="medium-blue-text">dedicated to having people</strong> and neighborhoods <strong class="medium-blue-text">safer</strong> in America.
				There are many threats in America today: ISIS, criminals, and other predators.
				Law enforcement, as good as they are, can only do so much.

			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="spacer-3"></div>

